        "text": "=Extract structured data from this conversation. Reply with ONLY valid JSON, no explanation, no markdown formatting, no backticks, no extra text.\n\nConversation: {{ $json.output }}\n\nReturn exactly this JSON shape:\n{\n  \"category\": \"Pothole\" or \"Garbage\" or \"Streetlight\" or \"Water\" or \"Other\",\n  \"urgency\": \"Low\" or \"Medium\" or \"High\",\n  \"location\": \"string\",\n  \"description\": \"one sentence summary of the issue\"\n}",
